	('8ae87b67-32e5-4d1f-b1f0-0edb48652957', 'Global Volunteer Waiver', '<p><strong>Volunteer Waiver & Release</strong></p><p>By signing below, I acknowledge that I am voluntarily participating in activities organized by Let''s Assist and assume all risks associated with participation. I agree to release and hold harmless Let''s Assist, its organizers, and affiliates from any and all liability for injury, loss, or damage arising from participation, except where prohibited by law.</p><p>I certify that the information provided is accurate and that I have read and understand this waiver.</p>', 1, true, '2026-01-19 07:38:00.772086+00', '2026-01-19 07:38:00.772086+00');
